                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2603.01840/2603.01840v1/figures/data.png",
                "caption": "Figure 3:Overview of the proposed data processing and optimization pipeline. This pipeline operates through five rigorous stages, including Geometry-Driven Feature Extraction and Dual Indexing, Stratified Sampling and Unified Re-annotation, Synthetic Data Generation for Structural Priors, Automated Quality Control and Hard-Negative Mining and Expert-Level Refinement via Model Distillation.",
